<style>
  .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
    width: calc(100% - 710px);
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
    width: 660px;
    height: 560px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 11px;
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image-border {
    border: 1px solid #3C1F1B;
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image-small {
    height: 440px;
  }
  .text-image-block_wrapp-image-contain {
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
      width: 550px;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
        width: calc(100% - 600px);
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .text-image-block_wrapp {
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .text-image-block .rebranding_container {
      padding: 0;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text {
      padding: 0 15px;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-text p {
      text-align: justify;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 0;
    }
    .text-image-block_wrapp-image-small {
      height: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="rebranding_container">
  <div class="text-image-block_wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-center-sb">
    <div class="text-image-block_wrapp-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <h2 class="h2-heading-ss w-100">
        Understanding    
        <span class="h2-heading-pp">
          authentic Louis Vuitton bags
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="body-text">
        Authentic Louis Vuitton bags are renowned for their exceptional quality, timeless design, and meticulous craftsmanship. One of the most iconic Louis Vuitton handbags is the Speedy bag, known for its unique stitching patterns, logo placement, and date codes. 
        <br><br>
        To ensure the authenticity of a Louis Vuitton bag, it’s essential to inspect the bag’s exterior and interior carefully. Look for the iconic Louis Vuitton monogram pattern, which is a key identifier of authentic Louis Vuitton bags. 
        <br><br>
        The monogram pattern should be symmetrical, with the LV logo centered and the four-petal fleur-de-lys and four-petal flower inside a circle motifs evenly spaced. This attention to detail is a hallmark of Louis Vuitton’s commitment to quality and authenticity.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img class="text-image-block_wrapp-image" src="{{ "lv_understanding.webp" | asset_url }}" alt="Understanding authentic Louis Vuitton bags">
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "SEO Text & image",
    "class": "text-image-block rebranding-wider-section-bottom rebranding-wider-section-bottom-image",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}